asakarma.sxml" एकं निराशाकर्म))(lit (a @n "XIV" @href "/sa/k/edgar-rice-burroughs/mangalasya-caturangah/gekasya-ajnaya.sxml" गेकस्य आज्ञया))(lit (a @n "XV" @href "/sa/k/edgar-rice-burroughs/mangalasya-caturangah/khanigartasya-vrddhah.sxml" खनिगर्तस्य वृद्धः))(lit (a @n "XVI" @href "/sa/k/edgar-rice-burroughs/mangalasya-caturangah/namantaraparivartanam.sxml" नामान्तरपरिवर्तनम्))(lit (a @n "XVII" @href "/sa/k/edgar-rice-burroughs/mangalasya-caturangah/mrtyum-prati-natakam.sxml" मृत्युं प्रति नाटकम्))(lit (a @n "XVIII" @href "/sa/k/edgar-rice-burroughs/mangalasya-caturangah/nisthayah-karyam.sxml" निष्ठायाः कार्यम्))(lit (a @n "XIX" @href "/sa/k/edgar-rice-burroughs/mangalasya-caturangah/mrtanam-bhayam.sxml" मृतानां भयम्))(lit (a @n "XX" @href "/sa/k/edgar-rice-burroughs/mangalasya-caturangah/bhirutvasya-aropah.sxml" भीरुत्वस्य आरोपः))(lit (a @n "XXI" @href "/sa/k/edgar-rice-burroughs/mangalasya-caturangah/premaya-jokhimah.sxml" प्रेमाय जोखिमः))(lit (a @n "XXII" @href "/sa/k/edgar-rice-burroughs/mangalasya-caturangah/vivahasamaye.sxml" विवाहसमये)))))